text: Alejandro Madorno (born 12 December 1971) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Buenos Aires
